title: Raymundo's Wedding Highlights + Bobby Brings TikTok Artist In Studio + Amy Shares Emotional Story Remembering Jerry Jeff Walker
itunes:title: Raymundo's Wedding Highlights + Bobby Brings TikTok Artist In Studio + Amy Shares Emotional Story Remembering Jerry Jeff Walker
description:
Our producer, Raymundo is now married! Bobby, Amy, Eddie and Lunchbox give their top moments from his wedding and Raymundo gives us all the details about his big day. Bobby brings in artist Sarabeth Taite who he saw on TikTok after making a video claiming she’d never been on the radio before or heard her music. Plus, we get into a debate after Amy has a story about Alan Jackson’s Top 5 Songs in her pile!
